							.news__more Explore More 
				li
					a.news__link(href="#")
						img(src="img/news-2.jpg", alt="")
						.news__inner
							.news__title The Best Family Cars
							.news__text The number of seats is just the tip of the iceberg. Learn what makes for the best family car, from advanced safety features to cargo spece and family...
							.news__more Explore More 
